{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2904","heading":"Establishment of Estuary Habitat Restoration Council","label":"2904 Establishment of Estuary Habitat Restoration Council","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/ch42","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments2007—Subsec. (b)(6) to (8). added pars. (6) to (8).Pub. L. 110–114"],"amendments":["Amendments2007—Subsec. (b)(6) to (8). added pars. (6) to (8).Pub. L. 110–114"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Council","label":"a Council","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"There is established a council to be known as the “Estuary Habitat Restoration Council”.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Duties","label":"b Duties","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"soliciting, reviewing, and evaluating project proposals and developing recommendations concerning such proposals based on the factors specified in ;section 2903(c)(3) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"submitting to the Secretary a list of recommended projects, including a recommended priority order and any recommendation as to whether a project should be carried out by the Secretary or by another Federal department or agency under ;section 2903(g) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"developing and transmitting to Congress a national strategy for restoration of estuary habitat;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"periodically reviewing the effectiveness of the national strategy in meeting the purposes of this chapter and, as necessary, updating the national strategy;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"providing advice on the development of the database, monitoring standards, and report required under sections 2906 and 2907 of this title;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"cooperating in the implementation of the strategy developed under ;section 2905 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":null,"label":"7","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"recommending standards for monitoring for restoration projects and contribution of project information to the database developed under ; andsection 2906 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"8","heading":null,"label":"8","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b/8","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fb%2F8","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"otherwise using the respective authorities of the Council members to carry out this chapter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Membership","label":"c Membership","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary (or the Secretary’s designee).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Under Secretary for Oceans and Atmosphere of the Department of Commerce (or the Under Secretary’s designee).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Administrator of the Environmental Protection Agency (or the Administrator’s designee).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fc%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of the Interior, acting through the Director of the United States Fish and Wildlife Service (or such Secretary’s designee).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fc%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Agriculture (or such Secretary’s designee).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fc%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The head of any other Federal agency designated by the President to serve as an ex officio member of the Council.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Prohibition of compensation","label":"d Prohibition of compensation","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Members of the Council may not receive compensation for their service as members of the Council.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Chairperson","label":"e Chairperson","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The chairperson shall be elected by the Council from among its members for a 3-year term, except that the first elected chairperson may serve a term of fewer than 3 years.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":"Convening of Council","label":"f Convening of Council","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"First meeting","label":"1 First meeting","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/f/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Ff%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall convene the first meeting of the Council not later than 60 days after , for the purpose of electing a chairperson.November 7, 2000","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Additional meetings","label":"2 Additional meetings","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/f/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Ff%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The chairperson shall convene additional meetings of the Council as often as appropriate to ensure that this chapter is fully carried out, but not less often than annually.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"g","heading":"Council procedures","label":"g Council procedures","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/g","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fg","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Council shall establish procedures for voting, the conduct of meetings, and other matters, as necessary.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"h","heading":"Public participation","label":"h Public participation","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/h","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fh","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Meetings of the Council shall be open to the public. The Council shall provide notice to the public of such meetings.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"i","heading":"Advice","label":"i Advice","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/i/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fi%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to assist the Council in the development of the estuary habitat restoration strategy to be developed under ; andsection 2905 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/i/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2904/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2904%2Fi%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to provide advice and recommendations to the Council on proposed estuary habitat restoration projects, including advice on the scientific merit, technical merit, and feasibility of a project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
